org.lukep.javavis.program.generic.models
Interface IGenericModelNode

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
IMeasurableNode
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClassModel, MethodModel, PackageModel, ProjectModel, VariableModel
public interface IGenericModelNode
extends java.io.Serializable

Represents a language agnostic abstract program entity obtained from the originally parsed object graph. Each model node has a list of Relationships with other models, and one parent in the tree structure.
